# Keep LF line endings in the repo AND working tree on every platform.
# Skills are plain text/markdown read identically by Claude Code and Cursor on
# Windows / macOS / Linux — forcing LF avoids spurious CRLF diffs across machines.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets: never apply EOL conversion.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
